maneuver.instruction: Enter A8/R2/Mombasa - Nairobi Road and take the 1st exit.
Keep right to take A8/E/Nairobi Expressway.
Turn right to take the ramp.
Enter Kenyatta Avenue Round About and take the 2nd exit onto A8/R2/Uhuru Highway.
Enter University Way Round About and take the 3rd exit onto University Way.
Enter Globe Roundabout and take the 2nd exit.
Your destination is on the left.
